node.text:
„Three Sheets to the wind“ by @cocktailsbyadam
•
1 oz @DenizenRum Merchant’s Reserve
½ oz @DenizenRum Vatted Dark
½ oz Fresh Lime Juice
½ oz Fresh Pineapple Juice
½ oz Passionfruit Purée
½ oz Coconut Cream
½ oz Demerara Syrup
2 dashes Aromatic Bitters
3 Fresh Blackberries
•
Recipe by @cocktailsbyadam
•

I know, you loved that cocktail by @@giorgiochiarello  as much as we did ❤️
So I decided to put it on Reels as well.
•
40ml @ronmillonarioperu
20ml liquore alla pesca
10ml sciroppo di lamponi
15ml succo di limone
Top soda water

Garnish:
Fiore / Lime essiccato
•
